name: Paper Boy Flyin' High
description:
The measurement of a good paper airplane is at how long it lasts in the air until the inevitable fall.
In Paper Boy Flyin' High you play as a paper airplane trying to deliver a message to far lands.

Avoid obstacles and try to reach as far as possible.
Use the arrow keys to guide the aircraft.
